edu.ucla.sspace.dv
Class PennTags

java.lang.Object
  edu.ucla.sspace.dv.PennTags

public final class PennTags
extends Object

A class containing information on the Penn Treebank part of speech (POS) tag set. This class is a utility for other classes that need to interact with objects on the basis of their part of speech category.
